      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0657P0-02237'>
        <a name='S5LV0657P0_20040114_GCR_202'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-lytton-cobbold' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0657P0_20040114_GCR_202' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Lytton Cobbold' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
