            The other point of real importance is that, if we were to remove the first half of someone's career from a professional directory&#x2014;which people buy as a reputable document&#x2014;what have we done in terms of the <a href="/acts/trade-descriptions-act-1968">Trade Descriptions Act 1968</a>? The alternative might be that, if such a person were determined on such a course they should not appear at all. That question relates sufficiently for me to ask the Minister for guidance.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
